&lt;li&gt;Demonstrate capacity to track and solve any plant incident&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Optimize the availability and performance ratio of the portfolio under supervision&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the line manager in the daily supervision and analysis of the portfolio technical performance and operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage the relationships with Operation &amp;amp; Maintenance contractors and Customer Interface on Technical Issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure all O&amp;amp;M / other technical service providers achieve, at a minimum, their contractual obligations&lt;/li&gt;
