&lt;li&gt;Ownership of issue resolution and prioritisation of tasks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supervise and manage outcomes of the site visits executed by the site managers, as well as post-construction punchlists&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supervise the control of the technical documentation related to the plants&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the other teams in providing regular compliance with the DNOs, insurance companies, Public Entities, etc;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Constant identification and implementation of process improvements&lt;/li&gt;
